OL,3,CPolice investigating after historic
OL,4,CNew Forest village hall vandalised
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after an
OL,7,Fhistoric village hall in the New
OL,8,FForest was vandalised.
OL,10,FBuilders had been renovating East
OL,11,FBoldre Village Hall, near Lymington,
OL,12,Flast week when it was left damaged and
OL,13,Fflooded after a break-in.
OL,15,FA number of items, including tools
OL,16,Fwere also stolen, according to
OL,17,FHampshire Police.
OL,19,FA spokesperson for the hall said the
OL,20,Fcost of repairs will add pressure to
OL,21,Fan "already tight budget".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
