OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776963955
OL,3,CPolice investigating after historic
OL,4,CNew Forest village hall vandalised
OL,6,F"The wanton vandalism damaged the
OL,7,Frecently installed fire alarm cables
OL,8,Fand electrical wiring and water pipes
OL,9,Fwere damaged resulting in a flood,"
OL,10,Fthe spokesperson added.
OL,12,FA fundraising page has been set up for
OL,13,Fanyone wishing to donate towards the
OL,14,Frepair costs.
OL,16,FPolice say they are establishing the
OL,17,F"full circumstances surrounding the
OL,18,Fburglary" and are appealing for any
OL,19,Fwitnesses to come forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
